<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<OrderCancelRQ>
    <Header>
        <ServiceName>BOOKSEAT</ServiceName>
        <AirLine>EY</AirLine>
    </Header>
    <Party>
        <Participant>
            <MarketingCarrier>
                <AirlineDesigCode>EY</AirlineDesigCode>
            </MarketingCarrier>
        </Participant>
        <Sender>
            <TravelAgency>
                <PseudoCityID>BJS247</PseudoCityID>
            </TravelAgency>
        </Sender>
    </Party>
    <Request>
        <BookingRef>
            <BookingID>HS6D3H</BookingID>
            <TypeCode>PNR</TypeCode>
        </BookingRef>
        <DataLists>
            <ServiceDefinitionList>
                <ServiceDefinition FlightSegmentRPH="1" TravelerRPH="1" >
                    <Detail RFIC="C" RFISC="0C1" SeatNumber="15C"/>
                    <PriceList>
                        <Pirce CurrencyCode="CNY">600</Pirce>
                        <Pirce CurrencyCode="CNY">600</Pirce>
                    </PriceList>
                    <Description>UNACCOMPANIED MINOR</Description>
                </ServiceDefinition>
            </ServiceDefinitionList>
        </DataLists>
    </Request>
</OrderCancelRQ>
